phpar0\qj{.}}}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{123.186}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E9_2E23_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E9_2E23_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Federal regulations adopted as rules }}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8212\'3f}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ penalties.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The department shall adopt as rules the substance of the federal regulations }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. pt.\~6}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. pt.\~8}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. pt.\~10}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. pt.\~11}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The department shall adopt as rules the substance of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. \'a76.88}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, to permit a manufacturer of alcoholic beverages, wine, or beer, or an agent of such manufacturer, to provide to a retailer without charge wine and beer coil cleaning services, including carbon dioxide filters and other necessary accessories to properly clean the coil and affix carbon dioxide filters. The rules shall provide that the manufacturer shall be responsible for paying the costs of any filters provided.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The department shall adopt as rules the substance of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. \'a76.99}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ to permit, only with the explicit consent of the retailer, a manufacturer or a wholesaler of alcoholic liquor, wine, or beer to reset or rearrange another manufacturer\u8217\'3fs or wholesaler\u8217\'3fs alcoholic beverage products.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The department shall adopt as rules the substance of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{27 C.F.R. \'a710.21}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ to prohibit a manufacturer or a wholesaler of alcoholic liquor, wine, or beer from offering or giving, directly or indirectly or through an affiliate, a retailer free trips, bonuses, or prizes based on sales of the manufacturer\u8217\'3fs or wholesaler\u8217\'3fs alcoholic beverage products.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A licensee or permittee who permits or assents to or is a party in any way to a violation or infringement of a rule adopted pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ is guilty of a violation of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. A violation of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall subject the licensee or permittee to the general penalties provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and shall constitute grounds for imposition of a civil penalty or suspension or revocation of the license or permit pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.39}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{85 Acts, ch 32, \'a777}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2006 Acts, ch 1061, \'a71}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2007 Acts, ch 22, \'a736}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2018 Acts, ch 1060, \'a770}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2019 Acts, ch 113, \'a758}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 19, \'a72454}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 31, \'a71}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{123.187}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E9_2E24_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E9_2E24_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Direct shipment of wine }}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8212\'3f}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ permit and requirements.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine manufacturer licensed or permitted pursuant to laws regulating alcoholic beverages in this state or another state may apply for a wine direct shipper permit, as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. For the purposes of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, a }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fwine manufacturer\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means a person who processes the fruit, vegetables, dandelions, clover, honey, or any combination of these ingredients, by fermentation into wines.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Only a wine manufacturer that holds a wine direct shipper permit issued pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall sell wine at retail for direct shipment to any person within this state. }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{This section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall not prohibit an authorized retail licensee from delivering wine pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.46A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine manufacturer applying for a wine direct shipper permit shall submit an application for the permit electronically, or in a manner prescribed by the director, accompanied by a true copy of the manufacturer\u8217\'3fs current alcoholic beverage license or permit issued by the state where the manufacturer is primarily located and a copy of the manufacturer\u8217\'3fs basic permit issued by the alcohol and tobacco tax and trade bureau of the United States department of the treasury.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An application submitted pursuant to paragraph }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fb\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall be accompanied by a permit fee in the amount of twenty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A permit issued pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ may be renewed annually by submitting a renewal application with the director in a manner prescribed by the director, accompanied by the twenty-five dollar permit fee.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The direct shipment of wine pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall be subject to the following requirements and restrictions:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Wine shall only be shipped to a resident of this state who is at least twenty-one years of age, for the resident\u8217\'3fs personal use and consumption and not for resale.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Wine subject to direct shipping shall be properly registered with the federal alcohol and tobacco tax and trade bureau, and fermented on the winery premises of the wine direct shipper permittee.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{All containers of wine shipped directly to a resident of this state shall be conspicuously labeled with the words \u8220\'3fCONTAINS ALCOHOL: SIGNATURE OF PERSON AGE 21 OR OLDER REQUIRED FOR DELIVERY\u8221\'3f or shall be conspicuously labeled with alternative wording preapproved by the director.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{All containers of wine shipped directly to a resident of this state shall be shipped by a holder of a wine carrier permit as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.188}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{e.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Shipment of wine pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ does not require a refund value for beverage container control purposes under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 455C}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine direct shipper permittee shall remit to the department an amount equivalent to the wine gallonage tax on wine subject to direct shipment at the rate specified in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.183}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ for deposit as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.183, subsections 2 and 3}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. The amount shall be remitted at the time and in the manner provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.184, subsection 2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and the ten percent penalty specified therein shall be applicable.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine direct shipper permittee shall be deemed to have consented to the jurisdiction of the department or any other agency or court in this state concerning enforcement of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and any related laws, rules, or regulations. A permit holder shall allow the department to perform an audit of shipping records upon request.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{6.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A violation of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall subject the permittee to the general penalties provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and shall constitute grounds for imposition of a civil penalty or suspension or revocation of the permit pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.39}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{96 Acts, ch 1101, \'a71}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.legis.iowa.gov/docs/acts//CH0000.pdf" }{\fldrslt \f5 \fs18{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf5{2003 Acts, 1st Ex, ch 2, \'a7158, 205}}}}}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2010 Acts, ch 1031, \'a7100}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2010 Acts, ch 1193, \'a7165}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2013 Acts, ch 35, \'a719}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2015 Acts, ch 11, \'a71}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2015 Acts, ch 104, \'a72}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2017 Acts, ch 119, \'a718}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2018 Acts, ch 1060, \'a771}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2019 Acts, ch 113, \'a759, 60}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2022 Acts, ch 1099, \'a784, 85, 88}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 19, \'a72455 \u8211\'3f 2457}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0\cbpat2{Referred to in }{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{\'a7123.32}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.35}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.46A}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.173}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.176}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.183}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.184}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.188}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{123.188}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E9_2E25_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E9_2E25_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Wine carrier }}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8212\'3f}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ permit and requirements.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A person desiring to deliver wine subject to direct shipment within this state pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.187}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or to deliver wine shipped to or by a wine auction permittee pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.173C}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall submit an application for a wine carrier permit electronically, or in a manner prescribed by the director, which shall be accompanied by a fee in the amount of one hundred dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The director may in accordance with }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ issue a wine carrier permit which shall be valid for one year from the date of issuance unless it is sooner suspended or revoked for a violation of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A permit issued pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ may be renewed annually by submitting a renewal application with the director in a manner prescribed by the director, accompanied by the one hundred dollar permit fee.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The delivery of wine pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall be subject to the following requirements and restrictions:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine carrier permittee shall not deliver wine to any person under twenty-one years of age, or to any person who either is or appears to be in an intoxicated state or condition.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine carrier permittee shall obtain valid proof of identity and age prior to delivery, and shall obtain the signature of an adult as a condition of delivery.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A wine carrier permittee shall maintain records of wine shipped which include the permit number and name of the wine manufacturer or wine auction permittee, quantity of wine shipped, recipient\u8217\'3fs name and address, and an electronic or paper form of signature from the recipient of the wine. Records shall be submitted to the department on a monthly basis in a form and manner to be determined by the department.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A violation of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall subject the permittee to the general penalties provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and shall constitute grounds for imposition of a civil penalty or suspension or revocation of the permit pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.39}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2019 Acts, ch 113, \'a761}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2020 Acts, ch 1063, \'a757}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 19, \'a72458, 2459}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2024 Acts, ch 1088, \'a710, 11}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0\cbpat2{Referred to in }{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{\'a7123.32}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 123.187}}}\par}}